/passione-e-quiete-al-maggio-musicale-fiorentino/\' /><link rel=\'next\' title=\'&#8220;Tristan and Isolde&#8221; at the Salle Pleyel\' href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2012/10/tristan-and-isolde-at-the-salle-pleyel/\' /><meta name="generator" content="WordPress 4.5.3" /><link rel="canonical" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/10/parigi-salle-pleyel-tristan-und-isolde/" /><link rel=\'shortlink\' href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/?p=41891\' /><link rel="alternate" type="application/json+oembed" href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gbopera.it%2F2012%2F10%2Fparigi-salle-pleyel-tristan-und-isolde%2F" /><link rel="alternate" type="text/xml+oembed" href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gbopera.it%2F2012%2F10%2Fparigi-salle-pleyel-tristan-und-isolde%2F&#038;format=xml" /><script type="text/javascript">function toggleLinkGrp(id){var e=document.getElementById(id);if(e.style.display==\'block\')e.style.display=\'none\';elsee.style.display=\'block\';}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Carrois%20Gothic:300,400,400italic,700,700italic&amp;subset=latin,cyrillic-ext,cyrillic,latin-ext" type="text/css" /><style type="text/css">h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6{font-family:"Carrois Gothic",Arial,sans-serif}</style><link rel="shortcut icon" href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/favicon.ico"><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" /><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon-76x76.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="76x76" /><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon-120x120.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="120x120" /><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon-152x152.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="152x152" /><!--[if IE 7]><link rel="stylesheet" href="http://www.gbop